                      Uposatha Moondays (Mahānikāya) [.ical]
              %p
                Open Google Calendar, find
                = succeed "," do
                  %strong Other calendars
                open the dropdown menu and select
                = succeed "." do
                  %strong Add by URL
                Paste the link in the window that appears.
                %br
                %img{ src: "http://splendidmoons.github.io/images/add-by-url.png", title: "Add By Url", style: "border: 1px solid #c4c4c4; padding: 5px;" }
